Class CustomEdgeBetweennessClusterer<V,E>

    public class CustomEdgeBetweennessClusterer<V,E>
extends java.lang.Object
implements org.apache.commons.collections15.Transformer<edu.uci.ics.jung.graph.Graph<V,E>,java.util.Set<java.util.Set<V>>>
    This is a simple adaption of the EdgeBetweennessClusterer.class of the JUNG 2.0 library. It's adapted to be capable to handle a customized Graph that uses the classes MyLink.class and MyNode.class.
